Q = \sqrt{\frac{j+l - \sqrt{(j-l)^{2}+4k^{2}}}{j+l+\sqrt{(j-l)^{2}+4k^{2}}}} 
j = q^{2}\sin^{2}\theta+p^{2}\sin^{2}\phi\cos^{2}\theta+\cos^{2}\phi\cos^{2}\theta  
l = p^{2}\cos^{2}\phi+\sin^{2}\phi  
k=(1-p^{2})\sin\phi\cos\phi\cos\theta 
